gui/

amespahdbidlsuite_gui.pro


Procedure for starting the AmesPAHdbIDLSuite Graphical User Interface.

Updated versions of the NASA Ames PAH IR Spectroscopic Database and more information can be found at: www.astrochemistry.org/pahdb.

Examples

Start the AmesPAHdbIDLSuite Graphical User Interface:

IDL> amespahdbidlsuite_gui
